OL,3,CThousands take part in Pride in London
OL,4,Cparade
OL,6,FThousands of activists have marched
OL,7,Fthrough London in the capital's LGBT+
OL,8,FPride parade as campaigners warned
OL,9,Frights were "being taken away from
OL,10,Ftrans people".
OL,12,FMayor of London Sir Sadiq Khan was
OL,13,Famong those at the front of the Pride
OL,14,Fin London march on Saturday and led
OL,15,Factivists in a chant of "Happy Pride".
OL,17,FOrganisers said pop superstar Madonna
OL,18,Fwould not be attending Pride in London
OL,19,Ffollowing speculation that the 67-year-
OL,20,Fold singer was going to appear at the
OL,21,Fevent's Trafalgar Square stage.
OL,26,@qD@MOUrD@MO]wD@YOUwD@eO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/15
