CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1783689573
OL,3,CThousands take part in Pride in London
OL,4,Cparade
OL,6,FSome people in Trafalgar Square were
OL,7,Fwearing Madonna T-shirts amid rumours
OL,8,Fthat the "Queen of Pop" would make an
OL,9,Fappearance.
OL,11,FPride in London posted on social
OL,12,Fmedia: "In response to the rumours, we
OL,13,Fcan confirm that Madonna will not be
OL,14,Fappearing or performing at Pride in
OL,15,FLondon.
OL,17,F"We have two fantastic headliners at
OL,18,FTrafalgar Square to conclude a
OL,19,Fbrilliant day of protest and
OL,20,Fcelebration."
OL,26,@pD@JOUpD@WO]tD@HOUyD@AOU|D@MO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
