CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1783689573
OL,3,CThousands take part in Pride in London
OL,4,Cparade
OL,6,FIt is understood that there had been
OL,7,Fcommunication between organisers and
OL,8,FMadonna but that she was never a
OL,9,Fconfirmed attendee.
OL,11,FAmong the musicians to appear in
OL,12,FTrafalgar Square were American singer-
OL,13,Fsongwriter Beth Ditto and Lewisham's
OL,14,FMNEK.
OL,16,FITV News London's Helen Keenan sat
OL,17,Fdown with MNEK on Friday ahead of his
OL,18,Fperformance at the weekend.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
