OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1783689573
OL,3,CThousands take part in Pride in London
OL,4,Cparade
OL,6,FMore than a million people were
OL,7,Fexpected to head into London for the
OL,8,Fcelebrations, with organisers saying
OL,9,Fmore than 35,000 marchers from more
OL,10,Fthan 600 groups were taking part in
OL,11,Fthe procession running from Hyde Park
OL,12,FCorner to Whitehall Place via
OL,13,FPiccadilly.
OL,15,FThe Metropolitan Police said before
OL,16,Fthe event that there would be "no
OL,17,Ftolerance of hate crime" as a busy
OL,18,Fweekend of Pride celebrations takes
OL,19,Fplace in the city.
OL,26,@xD@_OUyD@XO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/15
