PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1783689573
OL,3,CThousands take part in Pride in London
OL,4,Cparade
OL,6,FSpectators cheered as floats full of
OL,7,Fpeople dancing and speakers playing
OL,8,Fmusic drove through central London.
OL,10,FMany of those watching the parade wore
OL,11,Frainbow colours and carried Pride
OL,12,Fflags and fans on a hot sunny day in
OL,13,Fthe capital.
OL,15,FCompanies that sponsored floats at the
OL,16,Fparade included Lidl, Tesco and Ikea,
OL,17,Fwith the Swedish furniture brand's
OL,18,Ffloat carrying the message: "Love
OL,19,Fdoesn't require instructions."
OL,26,@zD@]OU{D@^O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
