OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1783689573
OL,3,CThousands take part in Pride in London
OL,4,Cparade
OL,6,FSpeaking at the march, Mr Tatchell
OL,7,Ftold the Press Association: "We're
OL,8,Fmarching in London Pride today to
OL,9,Fhighlight the fact that at the World
OL,10,FCup, which is ongoing right now, 11
OL,11,Fcountries ban gay footballers from
OL,12,Ftheir team ` that's against Fifa
OL,13,Frules, but Fifa is doing nothing."
OL,15,FThe Australian-born activist added:
OL,16,F"This year's Pride is as important as
OL,17,Fever.
OL,26,@oD@]OUuD@bO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1783689573
OL,3,CThousands take part in Pride in London
OL,4,Cparade
OL,6,F"Particularly now that Reform councils
OL,7,Facross the country are banning Pride
OL,8,Fflags ... wanting to remove books from
OL,9,Fshelves.
OL,11,F"That is very dangerous, very
OL,12,Fthreatening to all of us."
OL,14,FGay rights activist Julian Hows, 70,
OL,15,Fsaid the Pride in London march was
OL,16,Fimportant with "rights being taken
OL,17,Faway from trans people" in the UK.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUtD@ZO]xD@POUyD@WO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1783689573
OL,3,CThousands take part in Pride in London
OL,4,Cparade
OL,6,FSpeaking at the front of the parade,
OL,7,FMr Hows, 70, who was expelled from
OL,8,Fschool for early gay rights activism
OL,9,Fin 1971, told the Press Association:
OL,10,F"Pride is important every year.
OL,12,F"I've been coming to Pride marches
OL,13,Fsince 1972 when the policemen
OL,14,Foutnumbered the marchers."
OL,26,@rD@AOUtD@AOUvD@ZO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1783689573
OL,3,CThousands take part in Pride in London
OL,4,Cparade
OL,6,FMr Hows, who wore a rainbow-coloured
OL,7,Fwaistcoat with Abseil Against Section
OL,8,F28 and Gay Liberation Front pins,
OL,9,Fadded: "Pride is also important
OL,10,Fbecause it needs to have an underlying
OL,11,Flevel of protest, and you can see the
OL,12,Ffreedoms that we have can so easily be
OL,13,Ftaken away.
OL,15,F"We also always need to push further
OL,16,Fbecause there's always somewhere where
OL,17,Four rights are being taken away.
OL,26,@qD@HOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1783689573
OL,3,CThousands take part in Pride in London
OL,4,Cparade
OL,6,F"Whether it's in this country with
OL,7,FReform, whether it's this country with
OL,8,Frights being taken away from trans
OL,9,Fpeople, whether it's abroad in other
OL,10,Fcountries."
OL,12,FA spokesperson for Pride in London
OL,13,Fsaid: "The urgency is clear: NHS
OL,14,Fgender-affirming care waiting lists
OL,15,Fnow exceed four years in some regions
OL,16,Fwhile a comprehensive trans-inclusive
OL,17,Fban on conversion therapy remains
OL,18,Funcodified into law despite a 2018
OL,19,Fgovernment pledge.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@KO]uD@GOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1783689573
OL,3,CThousands take part in Pride in London
OL,4,Cparade
OL,6,F"At the same time, the community
OL,7,Finfrastructure LGBTQ+ people rely on
OL,8,Fis shrinking ` since 2006, 58% of
OL,9,FLondon's LGBTQ+ venues have closed.
OL,11,F"Together, these gaps in care,
OL,12,Fprotection and safe spaces are
OL,13,Funfolding amid continued hostility,
OL,14,Fwith Home Office figures showing that
OL,15,Fmore than 18,000 hate crimes motivated
OL,16,Fby sexual orientation were reported to
OL,17,Fpolice in 2025."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@PO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1783689573
OL,3,CThousands take part in Pride in London
OL,4,Cparade
OL,6,FPride in London interim chief
OL,7,Fexecutive Rebecca Paisis said: "We
OL,8,Fwant 2026 to be the most inclusive
OL,9,FPride in London event yet.
OL,11,F"Our movement has always been built on
OL,12,Fmany voices becoming one united front
OL,13,F` from the people who marched in 1972
OL,14,Fto those joining us for the first time
OL,15,Fthis year. That's where our power lies.
OL,17,F"As LGBTQ+ people, we've never been
OL,18,Fstrangers to adversity, but neither
OL,19,Fare we strangers to collective action.
OL,26,@oD@`OUsD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G13/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1783689573
OL,3,CThousands take part in Pride in London
OL,4,Cparade
OL,6,F"This year's campaign is a reminder
OL,7,Fthat whilst the community often faces
OL,8,Fchallenges in isolation, it is by
OL,9,Fcoming together that we can change
OL,10,Fhistory."
OL,12,FCo-founder of Stonewall and LGBT+
OL,13,Factivist Lisa Power said: "Adversity
OL,14,Fis meant to shatter us but it can make
OL,15,Fus stronger as it did in the 80s.
OL,17,F"Right now, we have a Government and
OL,18,Finstitutions meant to defend our
OL,19,Frights that are attacking trans
OL,20,Fpeople's rights, and the rest of ours
OL,21,Fwill follow."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@IO]uD@[OUyD@AOU}D@MO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G14/15
