OL,3,CThousands take part in Pride in London
OL,4,Cparade
OL,6,FPride in London is a majority
OL,7,Fvolunteer-led organisation responsible
OL,8,Ffor delivering the capital's flagship
OL,9,FLGBT+ Pride parade and events since
OL,10,F2013.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G15/15
